long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Elfeed.net extension lets you bookmark and save your preferred content from social media and websites with our user-friendly solution. You can later see them at elfeed.net.
Seamlessly curate content into feeds for easy organization and convenient access at a later time, share it with your friends and curate your digital life.
We have "native" (you'll see a button with our logo on these sites) integrations for several social media websites but you can save any tab by pressing the extension button!
